Package org.ginsim.gui.utils.data

Class ListPanelHelper<T,​L extends List<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ginsim.gui.utils.data.ListPanelHelper<T,​L>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of objects in the list
    L - list to extend
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AvatarParametersHelper, ListOfSimulationParametersHelper, PerturbationPanelListHelper, PriorityDefinitionHelper, PriorityManagerHelper
    public class ListPanelHelper<T,​L extends List<T>>
extends Object
    Provide configuration and helper methods for a list panel. The helper defines capability switches (reordering, adding, removing), GUI hints such as available actions, and methods to create new items.
    Author:
    Aurelien Naldi
